  <data name="textBoxDescription.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Main developer: Sprow-dev (Samuel Rowberry, sprowdev@gmail.com)

Credit to all contributors. View list on GitHub. (sprow-dev/WinTouchUp)
Thanks to them, this is possible for everybody.

Note from Sprow: I am an extremely busy full-stack developer. I would not have the time nor patience to do this if it was closed source.
I'm a lot more patient with people when I can set clear expectations. It lets me breathe and not deal with entitled brats.
My promise: For every contribution, even just a simple bug report, I will try to find 1 way to improve my code.

I can't promise that this is 100% human-written, but at least my part of it is.</value>
